{
  "id": "S2P05M32",
  "title": {
    "product_var": "ZPRODTSK",
    "text": "HOW TO RECORD A KEY MACRO",
    "version_var": "ZSHRTVER",
    "prefix": "HELP"
  },
  "type": "help",
  "body": {
    "rows": [
      {
        "type": "command",
        "variable": "ZCMD"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "So, if we wanted to create a \"C\" Comment-Box, we would want to"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "insert the text:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "/*-----------------------*/"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "/*                       */"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "/*-----------------------*/"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "To insert this text into the current document at the current"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "cursor position, we would first hit the Newline key to move"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "the cursor to the editor line command field, then hit"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "[CURSOR-UP] to move to the line we were just on, type the letter"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\"i\" on the line command field, and finally hit Enter."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "We have just recorded the sequence for insert a blank line."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Now, if we type \"/*-----------------------*/\" and follow that"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "with another Enter, a new blank line will open up for further"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "input.  Continue the process until the Comment Box is completed."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "field_row",
        "fields": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "(Press"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "content": "ENTER+to continue)"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
